# Firebase Admin SDK / service-account keys — NEVER commit.
# These are server secrets and belong only in Vercel env vars
# (FIREBASE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT). This pattern would have caught the
# sfgl-ad892-firebase-adminsdk-fbsvc-*.json leak.
*-adminsdk-*.json
firebase-adminsdk*.json
serviceAccount*.json
service-account*.json
*-service-account*.json
